Global Gas-Tumble Dryers Market Insights
Gas-Tumble Dryers Market size was valued at USD 5.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Gas-Tumble Dryers Market Overview
The gas-tumble dryers market has witnessed significant growth in recent years, with a market value projected to reach USD 12.5 billion by 2028, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.4% from 2023 to 2028. This growth is attributed to the rising demand for energy-efficient home appliances, an increase in consumer preference for gas-powered dryers due to their cost efficiency, and improvements in dryer technology. Additionally, the ongoing development in smart appliances and rising disposable incomes globally are expected to drive further expansion in the market.

